#### ** Classification Models**  
- **Logistic Regression** (Binary & Multi-Class)  
- **Naïve Bayes Classifier**  
  - **Gaussian Naïve Bayes** – Used for normally distributed data.  
  - **Multinomial Naïve Bayes** – Used for text classification & NLP.  
  - **Bernoulli Naïve Bayes** – Used for binary feature datasets.  
- **Decision Trees** (Entropy, Gini Index, Pruning Techniques)  
- **Random Forest Classifier** (Ensemble Learning)  
- **Support Vector Machine (SVM)** (Linear & Kernel-based)  
- Model Evaluation Metrics: **Accuracy, Precision, Recall, F1-score, AUC-ROC, Confusion Matrix**  

### ** Feature Selection & Model Optimization**  
- **L1 Regularization (Lasso Regression) for Feature Selection**  
